# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
/target/
/gen/schemas

# Output publish sidecar Portal (di-generate scripts/desktop-publish-portal.mjs).
# .gitkeep dipertahankan agar folder resources/portal selalu ada — tauri-build
# memvalidasi path resource saat compile (cargo check di clone segar tetap hijau).
/resources/portal/*
!/resources/portal/.gitkeep
